{"tid":2078869,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭敬基剪爛TVB員工證　向不續約藝員喊話：舊夢不須記！","createTime":"2020-06-25T11:17:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T00:54:21.000Z","uid":16659,"like":74,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f260bf089d290717a220deb52b3108153fb09eb2","tid":2078869,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:17:23.000Z","msg":"香港藝人鄭敬基1989年加入無綫（TVB），曾演出《烈火雄心》、《女人俱樂部》等劇集為人所熟知，後來傳因參與去年9月元朗遊行而不獲續約，連當時劇集《牛下女高音》播出也無緣參與宣傳活動，但鄭敬基為人豁達，一直沒有說TVB不是。今日（25日），他在Facebook上載一張把TVB員工證剪碎的照片並寫道：「致主動不續約或不被續約的演藝朋友們，反正世界沒有大台，不如站在香港人的一邊，一同齊上齊落爭取自己想要的天空。」最後又標籤「舊夢不須記」，告別在TVB的種種。"},{"pid":"da971ca9480a144f4fe73a21bffd7772c4f5a9ed","tid":2078869,"uid":16659,"like":49,"dislike":3,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:17:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200625/352888666403770368.jpeg/BB-G3t0xsSwv_iLerdh-9I4M7hkm7q44T1akL09WpC8?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200625%2F352888666403770368.jpeg%2FBB-G3t0xsSwv_iLerdh-9I4M7hkm7q44T1akL09WpC8%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=a171e071&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200625/352888668589002752.jpeg/FHR1c4Jm6Z8k5UjArpej8Mhpwe_7-nIl69jpGuvY6Ro?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200625%2F352888668589002752.jpeg%2FFHR1c4Jm6Z8k5UjArpej8Mhpwe_7-nIl69jpGuvY6Ro%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=fd1fc1b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n剪證師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c7b6167c2ecd7bfb800ae674c4061cc0c174f0c","tid":2078869,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:18:26.000Z","msg":"［行動po置頂］全民報哨<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2078606\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2078606</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"850a818b565578a0428ff7923735629d50